) in light of the intervening amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignating former par. (1) as (2), to reflect the probable intent of Congress. See below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (1) as (2). Former par. (2) redesignated (3)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (3). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (2) as (3). Former par. (3) redesignated (4)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “Tribe” for “tribe” in par. (4), could not be executed because the term “tribe” does not appear. See below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (3) as (4). Former par. (4) redesignated (5)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (5). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (4) as (5). Former par. (5) redesignated (6)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (5)(B)(i). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “Tribe” for “tribe” in par. (4), was executed by making the substitution in par. (5)(B)(i), in light of the intervening amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignating former par. (4) as (5), to reflect the probable intent of Congress. See above."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(2)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Tribes” for “tribes”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “The term ‘Indian Tribe’ has the meaning given the term ‘Indian tribe’ ” for “The term ‘Indian tribe’ has the meaning given that term” in par. (6), could not be executed because the phrase “The term ‘Indian tribe’ has the meaning given that term” does not appear. See below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (5) as (6). Former par. (6) redesignated (7)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (7). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “The term ‘Indian Tribe’ has the meaning given the term ‘Indian tribe’ ” for “The term ‘Indian tribe’ has the meaning given that term” in par. (6), was executed by making the substitution in par. (7) in light of the intervening amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignating former par. (6) as (7), to reflect the probable intent of Congress. See below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (6) as (7). Former par. (7) redesignated (9)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (8). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “Tribe” for “tribe” in par. (8), could not be executed because the term “tribe” does not appear. See below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(3)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (8). Former par. (8) redesignated (10)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (9). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (7) as (9). Former par. (9) redesignated (11)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (10). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Tribal” for “tribal”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/1/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(1)(A)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “Tribe” for “tribe” in par. (8), was executed by making the substitution in par. (10) in light of the intervening amendment by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignating former par. (8) as (10), to reflect the probable intent of Congress. See below."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (8) as (10)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Par. (11). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/e/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(e)(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “Tribal” for “tribal”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/261/s3/b/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–261, § 3(b)(1)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (9) as (11)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
